 51          if len(self) >= self.maxsize: 
 52              # maximum cache size exceeded, cull old items 
 53              # 
 54              # note queue is the real cache but its size is boundless 
 55              # since it might have duplicate references. 
 56              # 
 57              # don't bother culling if queue is smaller than weakref, 
 58              # this means there are too many references outside the 
 59              # cache, culling won't free much memory (if any). 
 60              while len(self) >= self.maxsize <= len(self.queue): 
 61                  cullsize = max(int(len(self.queue) / self.cullsize), 2) 
 62                  try: 
 63                      for i in range(cullsize):

 65                  except IndexError:
